      "content": "it just feels logical when i look at the numbers. like, if i wasn't here, the insurance would pay out, the debt would be smaller, and they could actually breathe. instead, they're stuck supporting me and my mistakes. it feels like the only way i actually help them is by not being a part of the equation anymore.",
